On the occasion of Sankranthi, Bapu Group of Institutions, Bapu Degree College had organised a fair on January 14. Students of the institution displayed their entrepreneurial skills by putting up stalls offering chats, traditional food items, fancy items, Mehndi stalls, caf√© and restaurants. Cultural programmes, 3D show and Scary House were organised as part of the event. The programme was inaugurated by the Bapu Group of Institution president Kamalamma along with college principal Dr. Venkata Reddy and Dean Rekha Sreeram. Large number of students and their parents participated in the event, said a college release.